openattic (2.0.2-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Merge GUI tree.
  * Remove left-over statoverride for /var/lib/openattic/ftp.
  * Add openattic-module-ceph package.
  * Drop dependency on libjs-angularjs.
  * Add build-depends to git, npm and apache2-dev.
  * Add dependency on python-requests.
